                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                        <img src="/get-on-gpay.png" alt="Google Play" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 120px;">
                        <img src="/pngwing.com.png" alt="App Store" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 120px;">
